snippet: Third-ranked Notre Dame defeated second-ranked UConn, extending its winning streak to 12 and ending the Huskies’ 57-game streak in the Big East.
abstract: College Basketball Women's Roundup; Notre Dame defeats Connecticut, 74-67; other results noted.
lead_paragraph: Third-ranked Notre Dame defeated second-ranked UConn, extending its winning streak to 12 and ending the Huskies’ 57-game streak in the Big East.
